    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in poor condition. It runs but has significant mechanical issues that will require substantial repair work in the near term. The exterior shows heavy scratches, dents, and other cosmetic damage. The interior is worn with visible damage to upholstery and trim. Best suited for someone willing to invest in repairs or looking for a parts vehicle.",
